{"tid":1106687,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(理性討論）想問下大家點睇神鬼","createTime":"2019-04-14T17:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T19:43:45.000Z","uid":234147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"430442f4a8926846a4d57fb4daf1368b82f1ceff","tid":1106687,"uid":234147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n呢排有個朋友講起就想問下大家意見<br />\n大家信唔信真係有神鬼佛呢樣野<br />\n我個人來講就信嘅<br />\n但係我對佢哋嘅理解<br />\n就係好似地球人同埋外星人果類感覺<br />\n但係我無親眼見過<br />\n見到有兩個朋友為左呢件事嘈到想打架咁樣<br />\n覺得好奇怪想問下大家點睇咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外我真係好悶同無咩朋友會同我傾呢個話題<br />\n大家有咩意見求分享"},{"pid":"edf71bc41bb21555c7f6374e18f7a54e9b8f581d","tid":1106687,"uid":234147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9af0a8178521636406d228040bedf35e599f680","tid":1106687,"uid":119916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"唔會絕對否定，不過覺得啲恐怖故都係節目吸收視作出嚟<br />\n至少自己未遇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7ab0e8fab721a8da69c380f05c2040c2496759","tid":1106687,"uid":234147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9af0a8178521636406d228040bedf35e599f680","tid":1106687,"uid":119916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"唔會絕對否定，不過覺得啲恐怖故都係節目吸收視作出嚟<br />\n至少自己未遇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"我都係咁覺得<br />\n恐怖片或者鬼屋嗰啲都係jump scare <br />\n睇恐怖片都係鍾意睇到心寒果種<br />\n講返神鬼先<br />\n如果有日遇到我都係應該會同佢傾下計咁<br />\n前提係佢唔係無啦啦找我晦氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1aafd3e38d5a3d9f07ef84f43850001245c6506","tid":1106687,"uid":234147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9af0a8178521636406d228040bedf35e599f680","tid":1106687,"uid":119916,"like":2,